{"tid":2043021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：香港已成抗威權橋頭堡 中國革命發源地 為保政權必不退讓","createTime":"2020-05-30T06:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T11:43:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":218,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"789fed1a95d6636ea2ccd27a302d8bb70fc0eca2","tid":2043021,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"人民日報警告反中亂港勢力等待可恥失敗<br />\n30.05.2020 14:18<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普批評全國人大通過制訂港區國安法，令香港變成一國一制，宣布啟動程序，撤銷對香港的特殊待遇。官方人民日報發表評論，指外國勢力與香港反中亂港勢力，公然鼓吹&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;&ldquo;自決&rdquo;&ldquo;公投&rdquo;等主張，把香港變成反中&ldquo;橋頭堡&rdquo;、&ldquo;顏色革命&rdquo;輸出地，如果還有人認為通過恐嚇要脅，就能迫使中國在主權、安全等核心利益上讓步，只能是痴心妄想，警告反中亂港的外部勢力，必將迎接堅決的反制，等待的只能是可恥的失敗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1294353&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1294353%26csid%3D261_367&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=a283d608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1294353&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"4d83cd6af2d31e082558c0f6c74b3101603d2878","tid":2043021,"uid":2054,"like":87,"dislike":4,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"Noted with laughing<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118f7c9a915a4ea54c455056e9c9200539ce8ece","tid":2043021,"uid":54126,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:54:08.000Z","msg":"burst into laughter"},{"pid":"3841b8e346b4fcd52fd713214b8f461fe745ff09","tid":2043021,"uid":183758,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"你咁講有機會了"},{"pid":"25210337f225d7599e04807346082b4641f2c3d9","tid":2043021,"uid":24944,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"官方驗證<img src=\"/asset